Package: SurfaceReconstruction
Type: Package
Title: An Incomplete Wrapper of the 'CGAL' C++ Library
Version: 0.0.9000
Author: Stéphane Laurent
Maintainer: Stéphane Laurent <laurent_step@outlook.fr>
Description: Partly wraps the 'CGAL' C++ library. Can perform convex hull construction and Delaunay tessellation in 2D or 3D, including elevated Delaunay triangulation, constrained 2D Delaunay triangulation, and provides some surface reconstruction techniques: Poisson surface reconstruction and advanced front surface reconstruction.
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.7), rgl, Rvcg
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppCGAL, RcppEigen
Suggests: onion, uniformly, misc3d, BH
SystemRequirements: C++ 14, gmp, mpfr
URL: https://github.com/stla/SurfaceReconstruction
BugReports: https://github.com/stla/SurfaceReconstruction/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: bzip2
